es, we can offer real solutions, such as bankruptcy and bankruptcy alternatives, including mortgage loan modifications and personal and small business reorganizations. Because the last thing you need to worry about when you are in debt is how to pay your lawyer, our office offers long-term payment plans. ', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 12:26:40', '2013-09-24 12:26:40', '', '29', 'http://localhost/brentbowen/29-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
